{"tid":1469934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《網絡兵法：不變應萬變》","createTime":"2019-08-14T03:38:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T03:52:54.000Z","uid":41705,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ca14918cc0ae6a5ed1328f0ac984ba479bf1bcd2","tid":1469934,"uid":41705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:38:18.000Z","msg":"論公關災難，任何品牌都有形象受損的時候。<br />\n<br />\n在商言商，我不建議遇事即出聲明。<br />\n<br />\n不論是澄清或道歉，說話前最好先看清局勢。<br />\n<br />\n根據個人工作經驗，絕大多數的公關問題，往往都可以簡單解決。<br />\n<br />\n真正的公關災難，通常是因為品牌主事者誠惶誠恐，以致胡亂應對，最終自招禍患。<br />\n<br />\n別人未罵你，自己就膽戰心驚，結果錯失了大事化小，小事化無的機會。<br />\n<br />\n我通常會對一眾老闆講：「驚閪咩？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nfrom 伍大師<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Loui5Ng/photos/a.409599812399442/3542777002415025/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FLoui5Ng%2Fphotos%2Fa.409599812399442%2F3542777002415025%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=0oBAxbMcX4V1PEKlHKxm0dTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=c629df7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Loui5Ng/photos/a.409599812399442/3542777002415025/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"a5e8c95d9563e5d442f65605a3cf900f0ebe51ce","tid":1469934,"uid":199257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:38:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b01e03a436c5e50c01dee0db4dd47d2b3d69ba4","tid":1469934,"uid":64946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:38:56.000Z","msg":"［前機場職員話你知 x 勸世文] 驕 兵 必 敗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468780\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468780</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f583042f9b1e93a949571c32596d06ad5630339b","tid":1469934,"uid":172292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:38:58.000Z","msg":"大師好嘢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae09683635d45b12b71fed680f5edf58f27c893e","tid":1469934,"uid":37894,"like":0,"disli